	instead of swap.
	* include/bits/regex_compiler.tcc (_Compiler<>::_M_quantifier):
	Likewise.
	* testsuite/28_regex/match_results/swap.cc: New testcase.

2015-01-08  Jonathan Wakely  <jwakely@redhat.com>

	PR libstdc++/60132
