	explicit_instantiation.cc: Use -Wno-deprecated.
	* testsuite/20_util/has_trivial_copy_assign/requirements/typedefs.cc:
	Likewise.
	* testsuite/20_util/has_trivial_copy_assign/value.cc: Likewise.
